ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCCOFTA Tariff Preference Regulations
PrecisCCOFTA TARIFF PREFERENCE REGULATIONS which allow eligible goods that are not shipped directly between Canada and Colombia to retain their eligibility for preferential tariff rates provided goods remain under customs control in third countries.
